---
import Layout from "@/layouts/main.astro"
import ContributeNav from "@/components/ContributeNav.astro"
---

<Layout
  title="Where Builders Meet | Scout guide"
  description="How to scout and share impressive guild bases in the Where Builders Meet community."
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl space-y-10">
    <ContributeNav current="scout" />

    <div class="space-y-2">
      <h1 class="font-heading text-2xl font-semibold">Scout guild bases</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">
        Found an impressive base? Help get it on the map.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="space-y-1.5">
        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-foreground">Found a base worth sharing?</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
          Use <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1 py-0.5 font-mono text-xs">/scout-guild</code> to report it. The command opens a short form: guild name and what to visit. The bot logs it to <span class="font-medium text-foreground">#guild-discoveries</span> for the community. You can also share screenshots manually there for more discussion.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-1.5">
        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-foreground">Know the builder? Make a new friend.</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
          Reach out and encourage them to submit it themselves with <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1 py-0.5 font-mono text-xs">/submit-guild</code>. They'll own their thread and can update it anytime: lore, screenshots, cover image, what to visit.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-1.5">
        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-foreground">Earn the Guild Cartographer role</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
          Moderators grant the <span class="font-medium text-foreground">Guild Cartographer</span> role to members who consistently scout and document guild bases across the community.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground border-t border-border pt-6">
      Any question? <a href="https://discord.gg/Qygt9u26Bn" class="underline hover:text-foreground transition-colors" data-umami-event="discord_cta_click">Ping us on Discord.</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</Layout>
